6: I don't have time for this!
17: How did you get this injury?
21:
This is... none of your business... More
importantly, the Titan... Argh!
28:
I know where we can find medical
supplies. Follow me.
34:
So he was betrayed by his own
comrades...
43:
The garrison my troops were
stationed at... Though now it's more
rubble than anything else.
47:
...I'm guessing you're the one who
patched me up.
50:
Sorry for the trouble. I appreciate it
though.
53: Where are Nimbus and his friends?
57:
Already gone. They're headed for
the Titan.
60:
Don't move around so much. Your
wound's deep. Open it back up, and
you might actually die.
64:
So what... Should I just sit back and
do nothing? I won't stand idly by
while everyone else risks their lives
to stop that thing!
68:
Are you telling me you can't control
it?
71:
...This might actually be the end of
the world.
76: Not if I can help it.
81:
Are you kidding? No regular person
can stand up to something like that...
86:
Doesn't matter how impossible it
seems. I still have to try!
89:
All of this is MY fault! I was helpless
to prevent it from happening...
97:
...You really think you're that much of
a bigshot, huh? That you're the ONLY
one who could've caused a
large-scale disaster like this.
100:
Whatever... Not like any of that
matters. It's all over for us.
104:
Haridal... Really? You're gonna give
up, just like that?
108:
After everything you've done... and
everything you still have to do?!
113: It's not like I WANT to give up!
117:
I didn't cut my brothers and sisters
down for everything to end up like
this...
120: But... what else can I do?
129: How can you carry on, despite it all...
135:
Rest at least for a little bit. I'm going
to prepare us a ride.
139:
Does that mean you're coming with
me?
143:
If I let you out of my sight again, who
knows what'll happen next?
147: Haha! You know me so well.
151: As expected of my best friend.
162:
Rashid? Should you be here? What
about your wound?
166:
...In all honesty, I'm not doing too
great.
169:
But this whole situation is my fault. I
have a responsibility to put an end
to it.
173: So please... Let me join you!
178:
Let me get this straight: you're
willing to risk your life outta a sense
of responsibility?
182: Well, not only that, of course.
185:
Mostly, I want to save Sotieth. She
doesn't deserve to be used as a
weapon to hurt other people!
190:
You know, you should've led with
that reason!
194:
Right... She matters to me... Maybe
more than I realized...
199:
Yeah? Then we better get her back
before you start gushing about your
feelings.
204:
I owe you more than I can ever
repay!
209:
I brought enough for all of us. Hop
on.
214:
Not good. That thing's going to fire
again!
217:
No! Not after we managed to get
this far!
226: Haha... She made it in time!
230:
Nephtim exists to crush the stars,
and shatter the night.
